Peter B. CHIAFALO, Levi Jennet Guerra, and Esther Virginia John, Petitioners,
v.
WASHINGTON. No. 19-465. Supreme Court of the United States. March 10, 2020. This case is no longer consolidated with No. 19-518, CO Dept. of State v. Baca, and one hour is allotted for oral argument in this case.
